<title>USA: Mesa Inc Q1 net rises.</title>
<headline>Mesa Inc Q1 net rises.</headline>
<dateline>IRVING, Texas 1997-04-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr			   $0.10		    $0.02</p>
<p> Net			  12,221		    1,057</p>
<p> Revs			 94,143		   80,643</p>
<p> Avg shrs		   64,280		   64,050</p>
<p>(All Data Above 000s Except Per Share Numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: Q1 1996 net inlcudes $6.8 million pre-tax charge for impairment of long-term assets.  Q1 1996 net includes $8.8 million pre-tax gain from investments and $2.5 million pretax gain from interest collection from Bicoastal Corp.</p>
<p>Preferred divs were $5.5 million vs none.</p>
